s%20may%20say%20wear%20it%20and%20go%20and%20they%20have%20to%20wear%20it.%20But%20everyone%20should%20study%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Suddenly%20Woken%20Up'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20are%20you%20empowering%20women%20by%20telling%20them%20what%20to%20wear%3F%20What%20girls%20want%20to%20wear%20should%20be%20left%20to%20them.%20Where%20is%20their%20choice%3F%20You%20have%20suddenly%20woken%20up%20that%20they%20are%20wearing%20it%3F%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20after%20so%20many%20years%20of%20independence%2C%20such%20a%20ban%20is%20being%20talked%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Kumar%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20college%20argued%20that%20the%20ban%20was%20also%20in%20place%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20students'%20religion%20was%20not%20disclosed%2C%20the%20court%20remarked%20that%20religion%20is%20revealed%20by%20names%20as%20well%20and%20stressed%20that%20such%20rules%20must%20not%20be%20imposed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20wearing%20a%20burqa%20could%20not%20be%20allowed%20as%20students%20could%20not%20sit%20in%20class%20like%20that%2C%20the%20court%20partially%20stayed%20the%20circular%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20issue%20notice%20in%20the%20week%20commencing%20November%2018.%20We%20partly%20stay%20the%20impugned%20circular%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20it%20directs%20that%20hijab%2C%20caps%20and%20badges%20will%20not%20be%20allowed.%20We%20hope%20and%20trust%20this%20interim%20order%20is%20not%20misused%20by%20anybody.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20girls%20had%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20after%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20had%20rejected%20their%20petition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723202160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Ftatqdjeo_supreme-court_625x300_08_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-college-hijab-ban-hijab-ban-how-are-you-empowering-women-top-court-raps-mumbai-college-for-hijab-ban-6300021%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Coming%20down%20heavily%20on%20a%20Mumbai%20college%20which%20had%20barred%20students%20from%20wearing%20burqas%20and%20hijab%20on%20campus%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20asked%20the%20institution's%20authorities%20how%20they%20were%20empowering%20women%20by%20telling%20them%20what%20to%20wear.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-college-hijab-ban-hijab-ban-how-are-you-empowering-women-top-court-raps-mumbai-college-for-hijab-ban-6300021%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCan't%20Jeopardise%20Careers%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Refuses%20To%20Postpone%20NEET-PG%20Exam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDismissing%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20a%20few%20students%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20refused%20to%20postpone%20the%20NEET-PG%20exam%20scheduled%20for%20Sunday%20and%20said%20it%20could%20not%20put%20the%20careers%20of%20nearly%202%20lakh%20candidates%20at%20risk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entrance%20exam%20for%20post-graduate%20medical%20courses%2C%20which%20was%20initially%20supposed%20to%20be%20held%20on%20June%2023%2C%20had%20already%20been%20postponed%20once%20as%20a%20precaution%20amid%20the%20row%20over%20the%20irregularities%20in%20NEET-UG.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeking%20that%20the%20NEET-PG%20exam%20be%20postponed%20again%2C%20the%20petitioners%20said%20many%20candidates%20appearing%20for%20the%20test%20have%20been%20allotted%20exam%20centres%20in%20cities%20where%20it%20was%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20reach.%20They%20said%20that%20the%20National%20Board%20of%20Examinations%20in%20Medical%20Sciences%20(NBEMS)%2C%20which%20conducts%20the%20exam%2C%20had%20informed%20them%20about%20the%20city%20where%20they%20would%20have%20to%20appear%20for%20the%20exam%20on%20July%2031.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfor