0to%20undergo%20a%20surgery%20soon%20after%20having%20pushed%20himself%20extremely%20hard%20to%20compete%20here%20while%20battling%20a%20constant%20fear%20of%20breaking%20down.%20Chopra%20was%20dealing%20with%20a%20nagging%20adductor%20niggle%20(a%20problem%20related%20to%20muscles%20in%20the%20thigh)%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%20Paris%20Games.%20But%20he%20managed%20a%20season's%20best%20effort%20of%2089.45m%20to%20secure%20a%20silver%20medal%2C%20making%20him%20the%20first%20track-and-field%20athlete%20from%20India%20to%20have%20two%20Olympic%20medals%2C%20the%20first%20being%20an%20unprecedented%20gold%20in%20Tokyo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20finished%20behind%20Pakistan's%20Arshad%20Nadeem%2C%20who%20stole%20the%20show%20with%20an%20Olympic%20record-shattering%20throw%20of%2092.97m%20to%20become%20the%20first%20individual%20Olympic%20gold-medallist%20from%20his%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20lot%20on%20my%20mind.%20When%20I%20am%20throwing%2C%2060-70%20percent%20focus%20of%20my%20is%20on%20the%20injury.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20get%20injured.%20Whenever%20I%20go%20for%20a%20throw%2C%20you%20will%20see%20that%20my%20speed%20is%20low.%20I%20am%20pushing%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20doctor%20told%20me%20to%20go%20for%20surgery%20but%20I%20didn't%20have%20that%20much%20time%20to%20take%20that%20decision%20before%20the%20world%20championship%20or%20after%20the%20world%20championship%20because%20it%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20Olympics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20the%202023%20world%20championship%20where%20he%20won%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2026-year-old%2C%20despite%20not%20being%20at%20his%20best%20here%2C%20became%20only%20the%20third%20Indian%20to%20win%20back-to-back%20Olympic%20medals%20after%20PV%20Sindhu%20and%20Sushil%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20still%20pushing%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20with%20a%20hint%20of%20frustration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20good%20in%20sport%2C%20it's%20not%20good%20to%20push%20and%20continue.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20run%20a%20long%20career%20then%20you%20have%20to%20be%20fit%20and%20healthy%20but%20there%20are%20competitions%20where%20you%20can't%20make%20a%20decision.%20Now%20we%20will%20work%20on%20this%20and%20work%20on%20the%20technique%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20said%20he%20will%20talk%20to%20his%20team%20and%20then%20%26quot%3Btake%20a%20decision%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20detailed%20how%20the%20last%20seven%20years%20have%20been%20tough%20for%20him%20as%20far%20as%20fitness%20is%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20this%20in%202017.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20treatments.%20But%20I%20will%20have%20to%20take%20a%20big%20decision%20for%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWon't%20find%20peace%20till%20I%20get%20a%20big%20throw%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20didn't%20mention%20the%2090m%20mark%20but%20Chopra%20said%20he%20has%20potential%20to%20achieve%20bigger%20throws.%20Chopra's%20career-best%20remains%2089.94m%20which%20was%20achieved%20back%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20distance%20that%20I%20had%20in%20me%20in%202016%2C%20especially%20in%202018%2C%20when%20I%20scored%20an%2088m%20in%20the%20Asian%20Games%2C%20after%20that%2C%20I%20feel%20that%20I%20still%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20throws%20left.%20So%2C%20until%20that%20happens%2C%20I%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20find%20peace.%20And%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20you%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20inside%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20without%20getting%20into%20the%20specifics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20will%20do%20it.%20I%20will%20keep%20my%20mind%20ready%20for%20the%20future.%20I%20will%20work%20on%20things.%20I%20will%20keep%20myself%20fit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaven't%20been%20able%20to%20throw%20as%20well%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%2C%20perhaps%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20talked%20about%20just%20how%20badly%20the%20niggle%20has%20affected%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20able%20to%20throw%20from%20a%20full%20runway.%20I%20have%20been%20throwing%20for%20the%20past%20year%20or%20two.%20Maximum%20throwers%20throw%2040-50%20in%20a%20session.%20It%20took%20me%202-3%20weeks%20to%20complete%20a%20session%20because%20there%20was%20a%20fear%20of%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20difficult.%20I%20am%20forcefully%20pulling%20it.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20explained%20that%20his%20lower%20body%20is%20as%20important%20as%20the%20throwing%20arm%20in%20getting%20the%20right%20elevation%20and%20speed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20body%20doesn't%20work%2C%20it%20won't%20help.%20I%20can%20go%20for%20a%20heavy%20and%20fast%20heave%20but%20when%20there%20is%20a%20broken%20leg%2C%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20technical%20things.%20It%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20throw%20with%20just%20the%20arm%2C%20to%20put%20all%20your%20power%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20gets%20wasted%20if%20the%20legs%20don't%20work%20properly.%20So%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20technical%20things.%20I%20will%20not%20go%20into%20it%2C%20you%20won't%20understand.%26quot%3B%20Chopra%20said%20he%20finds%20it%20painful%20to%20miss%20competitions%20because%20of%20fitness%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20coach%20always%20says%20that%20if%20you%20get%20a%20good%20blocking%20leg%20and%20a%20good%20groin%20then%20the%20throw%20will%20be%202-3-4%20meters%20ahead%20and%20then%20I%20have%20to%20send%20a%20message%20saying%2C%20'Sorry%2C%20I%20have%20to%20withdraw'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPersonally%2C%20I%20don't%20like%20it%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723201020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fi8p2lp6_neeraj-chopra-pti_625x30