20who%20will%20be%20represented%20by%20renowned%20senior%20counsels%20Harish%20Salve%20and%20Vidushpat%20Singhania%2C%20filed%20a%20plea%20before%20the%20CAS%20ad%20hoc%20division%20at%202%3A00%20PM%20on%20Friday.%20The%20CAS%20has%20confirmed%20that%20there%20was%20no%20time%20to%20annul%20her%20disqualification%20from%20the%20Olympic%20Games%2C%20due%20to%20the%20paucity%20of%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhogat%20then%20asked%20for%20a%20joint-silver%20medal%20to%20be%20issued%20to%20her%20in%20thee%2050kg%20women's%20freestyle%20wrestling%20category.%20A%20decision%20on%20the%20matter%20is%20likely%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Olympic%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECAS%20Statement%20On%20Vinesh%20Phogat's%20Plea%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20application%20was%20filed%20at%20the%20CAS%20Ad%20hoc%20Division%20at%2016%3A45%20CEST%20on%207%20August%202024%20by%20Indian%20wrestler%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20(the%20Applicant)%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20decision%20taken%20by%20United%20World%20Wrestling%20(UWW)%20to%20replace%20her%2C%20because%20of%20her%20failed%20second%20weigh-in%2C%20before%20the%20gold%20medal%20match%20of%20the%20Women's%20Freestyle%2050kg%20competition%20at%20the%20Olympic%20Games%20Paris%202024%20that%20was%20due%20to%20commence%20at%2018%3A15%20CEST%20the%20same%20day%20(the%20Challenged%20Decision)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20from%20the%20CAS%2C%20issued%20on%20Friday%2C%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Applicant%20initially%20sought%20a%20decision%20from%20the%20CAS%20Ad%20hoc%20Division%20annulling%20the%20Challenged%20Decision%20and%20ordering%20another%20weigh-in%20before%20the%20final%20match%20as%20well%20as%20a%20declaration%20that%20she%20be%20declared%20eligible%20and%20qualified%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20she%20did%20not%20request%20urgent%20interim%20measures.%20The%20CAS%20Ad%20hoc%20Division%20procedure%20is%20fast%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20possible%20for%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20merits%20to%20be%20issued%20within%20an%20hour%2C%20bearing%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20Respondent%20UWW%20would%20have%20had%20to%20be%20heard%20first.%20The%20procedure%20is%2C%20however%2C%20ongoing%20and%20the%20Applicant%20has%20confirmed%20that%20she%20seeks%20the%20annulment%20of%20the%20Challenged%20Decision%20and%20that%20she%20requests%20to%20be%20awarded%20a%20(shared)%20silver%20medal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20matter%20has%20been%20referred%20to%20the%20Hon.%20Dr%20Annabelle%20Bennett%20AC%20SC%20(AUS)%2C%20sitting%20as%20a%20Sole%20Arbitrator%2C%20who%20will%20hold%20a%20hearing%20with%20the%20parties%20today.%20The%20Sole%20Arbitrator's%20decision%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20issued%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Olympic%20Games%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association%20(IOA)%20is%20assisting%20Vinesh%20with%20her%20appeal%20after%20she%20was%20disqualified%20from%20the%20competition%20for%20being%20100gm%20over%20the%20stipulated%2050kg%20on%20the%20second%20day%20of%20her%20competition.%20She%20had%20made%20the%20weight%20on%20the%20first%20day%20and%20won%20three%20bouts%20on%20her%20way%20to%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnited%20World%20Wrestling%20(UWW)%20competition%20rules%20stipulate%20that%20a%20wrestler's%20results%20would%20be%20annulled%20if%20he%20(or%20she)%20does%20not%20make%20the%20weight%20on%20either%20day%20of%20competition.%20IOA%20President%20Dr%20PT%20Usha%20and%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20President%20Sanjay%20Singh%20had%20requested%20UWW%20President%20Nenad%20Lalovic%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20not%20annul%20Vinesh's%20results%20from%20the%20first%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20Inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723199880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F7356ds3k_vinesh-phogat-ani_640x480_09_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fit-wasnt-possible-for-a-decision-cas-issues-statement-on-vinesh-phogats-appeal-6298947%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CAS%20said%20that%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20issue%20verdict%20on%20Vinesh%20Phogat's%20appeal%20before%20the%20end%20of%20Paris%20Olympics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fit-wasnt-possible-for-a-decision-cas-issues-statement-on-vinesh-phogats-appeal-6298947%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20How%20Sanjay%20Dutt%20Became%20South's%20Favourite%20'Villain'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fble036ro_sanjay-dutt_625x300_09_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20director%20Prashanth%20Neel%20signed%20on%20Hindi%20actor%20Sanjay%20Dutt%20for%20%3Cem%3EKGF%20Chapter%202%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20no%20one%20thought%20much%20of%20it.%20In%20fact%2C%20Neel's%20casting%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EKhalnayak%20%3C%2Fem%3Estar%20as%20'Adheera'%20was%20peculiar.%20The%2065-year-old%20Sanjay%20Dutt%2C%20who%20made%20his%20stunning%20debut%20over%20four%20decades%20back%20with%20%3Cem%3ERocky%20%3C%2Fem%3E(1981)%2C%20had%20played%20everything%20from%20Bollywood%20hero%20to%20villain%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20his%20career%20had%20been%20in%20the%20doldrums%20for%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20But%3Cem%3E%20KGF%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20proved%20to%20be%20an%20unexpected%20turning%20point.%20'Adheera'%20turned%20Dutt%20into%20one%20of%20South%20cinema's%20most%20sought-after%20'villains'.%20But%20why%2C%20and%20how%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaking%20A%20Pan-Indian%20Film%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20cinema%20has%20long%20had%20a%20propensity%20for%20signing%20on%20Hindi%20actors%20to%20play%20the%20anti-hero%3A%20Sonu%20Sood%2C%20Jackie%20Shroff%2C%20Arjun%20Rampal%2C%20Akshay%20Kumar%2C%20Neil%20Nitin%20Mukesh%2C%20are%20just%20a%20few%20examples.%20But%20'Sanju%20Baba'%20seems%20to%20have%20outshone%20most%20others.%20%26quot%3BFilmmakers%20here%20believe%20that%20the%20audience%20gets%20bored%20of%20seeing%20the%20same%20old%20villains%20from%20their%20respective%20film%20industries.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20pan-India%20cinema%20is%20seeing%20them%20cast%20actors%20from%20across%20industries.%20So%2C%20if%20they%20have%20a%20familiar%20face%20from%20Bollywood%2C%20it%20will%20help%20them%20promote%20their%20film%20in%20Hindi%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Bhargavi%2C%20who%20tracks%20the%20Kannada%20film%20industry.%20Dutt's%20gritty%20roles%20in%20the%20past%20have%20something%20to%20do%20here%20too.%20%26quot%3BHis%20%3Cem%3EKhalnayak%20%3C%2Fem%3Emade%20a%20major%20impact%20and%20it%20was%20easier%20to%20convince%20the%20audience%20that%20he's%20a%20badass%20villain.%20The%20way%20Prashanth%20Neel%20presented%20him%20on%20screen%20made%20him%20more%20famous%2C%20and%20all%20the%20neighbouring%20South%20industries%20wanted%20to%20follow%20the%20same%20route.%20It%20was%20probably%20'FOMO'%2C%20or%20a%20belief%20that%20'if%20we%20have%20Sanjay%20Dutt%20in%20our%20film%2C%20even%20our%20film%20will%20be%20as%20successful%20as%20%3Cem%3EKGF%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%26quot%3B%20Bhargavi%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost-%3Cem%3EKGF%202%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Dutt%20went%20on%20to%20play%20a%20villain%20in%20%3Cem%3ELeo%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Tamil%20film%20starring%20Thalapathy%20Vijay%20and%20directed%20by%20Lokesh%20Kanagaraj.%20Essaying%20the%20role%20of%20Anthony%20Das%2C%20Dutt%20was%20as%20intense%20and%20ruthless%20in%20%3Cem%3ELeo%20%3C%2Fem%3Eas%20the%20fierce%20and%20menacing%20Adheera%20in%20%3Cem%3EKGF%202%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3Cem%3ELeo%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecemented%20Dutt's%20position%20as%20a%20larger-than-life%20antihero%20who%20had%20both%20the%20physique%20and%20persona%20to%20take%20on%20a%20South%20star.%20Dutt's%20are%20not%20villains%20who%20are%20'weak'%20or%20unconvincing%3B%20his%20age%2C%20experience%20and%20screen%20presence%20allow%20South%20directors%20to%20create%20roles%20that%20he%20can%20pull%20off%20with%20elan.%20Atlee%2C%20too%2C%20roped%20him%20in%20for%20a%20cameo%20in%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20%3Cem%3EJawan%3C%2Fem%3E%2Cand%20though%20Dutt%20played%20a%20cop%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20filmmaker%20wanted%20him%20in%20the%20film%20showed%20how%20popular%20the%20Hindi%20actor%20has%20become%20with%20South%20filmmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Irony%20Of%20Dutt's%20Past%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20hindsight%2C%20it%20now%20seems%20ironic%20how%20Dutt's%20bad-boy%20persona%20off-screen%2C%20which%20he%20consciously%20tried%20to%20change%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20or%20so%2C%20affected%20his%20Hindi%20film%20career.%20To%20many%2C%20Rajkumar%20Hirani's%202018%20film%2C%20%3Cem%3ESanju%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20dramatised%20biopic%20of%20the%20Rocky%20star%2C%20seemed%20like%20an%20attempt%20to%20redeem%20Dutt's%20past.%20And%20yet%2C%20today%2C%20it's%20this%20very%20'%20bad%20boy'%20image%20which%20Dutt%20tried%20so%20hard%20to%20shed%20that%20has%20made%20him%20South's%20favourite%20antihero.%20Dutt%20himself%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20the%20mood%20for%20something%20new.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20risk%20that%20I%20took%20in%20my%20career%20when%20I%20played%20characters%20with%20different%20shades.%20It%20paid%20off%20because%20I%20was%20convinced%20that%20I%20could%20challenge%20myself%20as%20an%20actor.%20If%20I'm%20not%20convinced%2C%20then%20how%20will%20audiences%20be%20convinced%3F%20It%20was%20when%20I%20did%20%3Cem%3EKhalnayak%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20I%20realised%20that%20I%20should%20look%20for%20roles%20out%20of%20my%20comfort%20zone%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20actor%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20in%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECome%20August%2015%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EMunna%20Bhai%3C%2Fem%3E%20star%20will%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20'baddie'%20again%20in%20the%20Telugu%20film%20%3Cem%3EDouble%20iSmart%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20directed%20by%20Puri%20Jagannadh%20and%20starring%20Ram%20Pothineni.%20Another%20South%20film%20that%20will%20see%20Dutt%20essay%20a%20negative%20role%20is%20the%20highly%20anticipated%20%3Cem%3EKD%3A%20The%20Devil%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20be%20exciting%20to%20see%20Sanju%20Baba%20as%20Dhak%20Deva%20in%20%3Cem%3EKD%3A%20The%20Devil%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20first%20look%20had%20the%20audience%20hooked%3B%20it%20seems%20like%20he's%20playing%20a%20villain%20with%20a%20comical%20edge%2C%20which%20is%20something%20right%20up%20his%20alley.%20I%20still%20remember%20how%20brilliantly%20he%20balanced%20menace%20and%20humour%20in%20%3Cem%3EAgneepath%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20have%20a%20feeling%20that%20director%20Prem%20will%20tap%20into%20that%20same%20energy%2C%20blending%20the%20intensity%20of%20%3Cem%3EAgneepath%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20the%20charm%20of%20%3Cem%3EMunna%20Bhai%20MBBS%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20Kannada%20audience%20is%20in%20for%20a%20treat%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Bhargavi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Spirit%20Of%20Experimentation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20song%20launch%20in%20Hyderabad%20this%20week%2C%20Dutt%20spoke%20about%20why%20he%20loved%20playing%20a%20villain%20in%20South%20films%3A%20it%20allowed%20him%20to%20explore%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20emotions.%20That%20works%20well%20for%20the%20South%20industry%20too%2C%20which%20isn't%20scared%20to%20%26quot%3Bexperiment%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIn%20South%20cinema%2C%20the%20villain%20has%20shades%20and%20a%20character%20arc%20-%20he%20is%20not%20a%20template%20'bad%20guy'%20who%20just%20goes%20around%20beating%20or%20killing%20people.%20We%20want%20the%20villains%20here%20to%20be%20larger-than-life%20and%20yet%20different%20in%20every%20film%20-%20so%20we%20experiment%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20a%20Tamil%20film%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20Dutt's%20newfound%20glory%20in%20the%20South%20has%20given%20a%20fillip%20to%20his%20overall%20career.%20He%20has%20five%20films%20lined%20up%20this%20year.%20Two%20years%20back%2C%20shortly%20after%20the%20success%20of%20%3Cem%3EKGF%202%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Dutt%20revealed%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20the%20film%20was%20his%20first-ever%20offer%20from%20the%20South.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20why%20%5BI%20was%20never%20approached%20before%5D.%20I%20believe%20there%20is%20no%20segmentation%20today%20as%20the%20whole%20industry%20is%20one%20big%20family%2C%20which%20is%20a%20good%20thing%20for%20Indian%20cinema.%20We%20now%20represent%20the%20Indian%20film%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Going%20by%20the%20roles%20he's%20essaying%2C%20Dutt's%20resurrection%20as%20a%20star%20villain%20is%20symbolic%20of%20not%20just%20the%20emergence%20of%20a%20new%20Indian%20film%20industry%2C%20but%20also%20the%20arrival%20of%20a%20new-age%2C%20kick-ass%20Indian%20villain%20who%20is%20more%20than%20just%20guns%20and%20swank.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20senior%20entertainment%20journalist%20and%20film%20critic)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723199880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Flng54q78_sanjay-dutt_625x300_09_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-bollywoods-sanjay-dutt-aka-sanju-baba-became-souths-favourite-villain-6299625%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Going%20by%20the%20roles%20he's%20essaying%2C%20Dutt's%20resurrection%20as%20a%20star%20is%20symbolic%20of%20not%20just%20the%20emergence%20of%20a%20new%20Indian%20film%20industry%2C%20but%20also%20the%20arrival%20of%20a%20new-age%2C%20kick-ass%20Indian%20villain%20who%20is%20more%20than%20just%20guns%20and%20swank.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-bollywoods-sanjay-dutt-aka-sanju-baba-became-souths-favourite-villain-6299625%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20Forms%20Panel%20To%20Ensure%20Safety%20Of%20Indians%2C%20Minorities%20In%20Bangladesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20centre%20has%20formed%20a%20committee%20to%20monitor%20the%20situation%20in%20Bangladesh%20amid%20reports%20of%20targeted%20violence%20against%20minorities.%20The%20committee%20will%20also%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20Indians%20and%20other%20minorities%20in%20the%20country%20amid%20deadly%20protests%20that%20saw%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20government.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20constituted%20a%20Committee%20to%20monitor%20the%20current%20situation%20on%20Indo-Bangladesh%20Border%20(IBB).%20The%20committee%20will%20maintain%20communication%20channels%20with%20their%20counterpart%20authorities%20in%20Bangladesh%20to%20ensure%20safety%20of%20Indian%20citizens%20and%20people%20belonging%20to%20minority%20communities%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Committee%20will%20be%20headed%20by%20ADG%2C%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%2C%20Eastern%20Command%20and%20will%20have%20IG%2C%20BSF%20Frontier%20HQ%20South%20Bengal%2C%20IG%2C%20BSF%20Frontier%20HQ%20Tripura%2C%20Member%20(Planning%20%26amp%3B%20Development)%2C%20Land%20Ports%20Authority%20of%20India%20(LPAI)%2C%20and%2C%20Secretary%2C%20LPAI%2C%20as%20its%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%20winner%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20was%20sworn%20into%20office%20as%20Bangladesh's%20interim%20leader%2C%20vowing%20to%20guide%20the%20country%20back%20to%20democracy%20after%20a%20student-led%20uprising%20ended%20the%2015-year%20rule%20of%20Sheikh%20Hasina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yunus%2C%20who%20returned%20to%20Dhaka%20from%20Europe%2C%20called%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20order%20in%20the%20South%20Asian%20nation%20after%20weeks%20of%20violence%20that%20left%20at%20least%20455%20people%20dead%2C%20calling%20on%20citizens%20to%20guard%20each%20other%2C%20including%20minorities%20who%20came%20under%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLaw%20and%20order%20is%20our%20first%20task...%20We%20cannot%20take%20a%20step%20forward%20unless%20we%20fix%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caretaker%20administration%20is%20a%20civilian%20team%2C%20bar%20one%20retired%20brigadier-general.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20call%20to%20the%20people%20is%20if%20you%20have%20trust%20in%20me%2C%20then%20make%20sure%20there%20will%20be%20no%20attacks%20against%20anyone%2C%20anywhere%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20said%2084-year-old%20Mr%20Yunus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20person%20is%20our%20brother...%20our%20task%20is%20to%20protect%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yunus%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20whole%20of%20Bangladesh%20is%20one%20big%20family%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20extended%20his%20best%20wishes%20to%20Bangladesh's%20caretaker%20leader%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20and%20called%20for%20the%20safety%20and%20protection%20of%20Hindus%20and%20other%20minority%20communities%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20best%20wishes%20to%20Professor%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20on%20the%20assumption%20of%20his%20new%20responsibilities.%20We%20hope%20for%20an%20early%20return%20to%20normalcy%2C%20ensuring%20the%20safety%20and%20protection%20of%20Hindus%20and%20all%20other%20minority%20communities.%20India%20remains%20committed%20to%20working%20with%20Bangladesh%20to%20fulfil%20the%20shared%20aspirations%20of%20both%20our%20peoples%20for%20peace%2C%20security%20and%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20wrote%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hasina%2C%20accused%20of%20widespread%20human%20rights%20abuses%20including%20the%20jailing%20of%20her%20political%20opponents%2C%20was%20forced%20to%20flee%20to%20neighbouring%20India%20on%20Monday%20as%20masses%20of%20protesters%20flooded%20Dhaka's%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonday's%20events%20were%20the%20culmination%20of%20more%20than%20a%20month%20of%20unrest%2C%20which%20began%20as%20protests%20against%20a%20quota%20plan%20for%20government%20jobs%20but%20morphed%20into%20an%20anti-Hasina%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20then%20agreed%20to%20student%20demands%20that%20Mr%20Yunus%20--%20who%20won%20the%20Nobel%20prize%20in%202006%20for%20his%20pioneering%20microfinancing%20work%20--%20lead%20an%20interim%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723199220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fd3t8m64g_bangladesh-protests-reuters_625x300_07_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-forms-panel-to-ensure-safety-of-indians-minorities-in-bangladesh-6299771%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20centre%20has%20formed%20a%20committee%20to%20monitor%20the%20situation%20in%20Bangladesh%20amid%20reports%20of%20targeted%20violence%20against%20minorities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-forms-panel-to-ensure-safety-of-indians-minorities-in-bangladesh-6299771%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mozambique%20ex-minister%20guilty%20of%20one%20of%20Africa's%20biggest%20corruption%20scandals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723199097000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fcde8%2Flive%2Fef04b810-5624-11ef-b082-713963fa2c72.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2F