.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20achieving%20energy%20efficiency%20using%20green%20fuels%2C%20Lohia%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20have%20turbines%20at%20Hapur%20that%20extract%20energy%20from%20the%20biomass%20furnaces.%20Their%20efficiency%20is%20increased%20following%20some%20retrofitting%20processes.%20A%20similar%20automation%20is%20done%20for%20heating%20and%20cooling%20systems.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20the%20motors%20at%20Merino%20Industries%20have%20been%20upgraded%20to%20IE3%20technology%2C%20which%20promises%20premium%20efficiency%20while%20being%20environmentally%20friendly.%20Meanwhile%2C%20through%20the%2010.59%20MW%20solar%20power%20system%2C%20approximately%2012.77%20million%20kWh%20units%20of%20electrical%20energy%20are%20generated%20%E2%80%94%20which%20accounts%20for%20around%2024%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20electrical%20energy%20requirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20features%20of%20Merino%E2%80%99s%20energy%20source%20include%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ea)%20Procurement%20from%20the%20local%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Eb)%20Production%20of%20around%20one%20million%20gigajoules%20of%20energy%20(FY2023-24)%2C%20meeting%20the%20heat%20requirements%20of%20its%20processing%20units%20in%20Hapur%20(Uttar%20Pradesh)%20and%20Rohad%20(Haryana)%20through%20complete%20combustion%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ec)%20Reduction%20of%20GHG%20emissions%20by%20approximately%2095%2C000%20MT%20of%20CO2%20equivalent%2C%20which%20would%20have%20otherwise%20been%20generated%20from%20burning%20fossil%20fuels%20like%20coal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ed)%20Pioneering%20the%20use%20of%20biomass%20since%202005%20and%20turbine%20technology%20in%20Hapur%20which%20extracts%20energy%20in%20electrical%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-m