duction%20in%20additional%20land%20available%2C%20at%20Merino%2C%20green%20practices%20have%20always%20been%20the%20priority.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20the%20development%20of%20Miyawaki%20forests%20(multi-layered%20forests%20consisting%20of%20native%20plant%20species)%20on%20the%20campus%20at%20Hapur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20that%20trees%20are%20integral%20for%20clean%20air%2C%20habitat%20preservation%2C%20livelihoods%2C%20watershed%20protection%2C%20soil%20erosion%20prevention%2C%20and%20climate%20change%20mitigation%2C%20Merino%20has%20set%20a%20target%20to%20increase%20green%20cover%20both%20within%20and%20outside%20factory%20premises%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20planting%20of%20over%2020%2C000%20tree%20saplings%20throughout%20India%20during%202023-2024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20is%20to%20evolve%20as%20an%20industry%20but%20to%20do%20so%20sustainably.%20By%20blending%20expertise%20and%20resources%2C%20the%20company%20believes%20positive%20transformations%20can%20be%20driven%20in%20society.%20%E2%80%9COur%20strong%20belief%20is%20that%20by%20prioritising%20people%2C%20the%20planet%2C%20and%20sustainable%20product%20offerings%2C%20enterprises%20can%20thrive%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Lohia%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723198670000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-1723194040.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D360474%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sustainability%20at%20Merino%20Industries%20is%20viewed%20as%20a%20mindset%20rather%20than%20an%20end%20goal%2C%20driving%20their%20commitment%20to%20eco-friendly%20practices%20and%20renewable%20energy%20alternatives.%20Their%20efforts%20have%20led%20to%2074.6%25%20of%20energy%20needs%20being%20met%20through%20green%20sources.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%2