been%20accused%20of%20receiving%20kickbacks%20while%20handing%20out%20liquor%20permits.%20The%20party's%20boss%20and%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20been%20in%20jail%20over%20the%20same%20charges%20since%20March%2C%20save%20for%20a%20brief%20period%20when%20he%20was%20released%20to%20campaign%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723190340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F09840o7o_manish-sisodia_625x300_09_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-benefit-arvind-kejriwal-case-too-manish-sisodia-lawyer-on-bail-order-6298892%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AAP%20leader%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20granted%20bail%20in%20a%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20walk%20out%20of%20jail%20today%20or%20tomorrow.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-benefit-arvind-kejriwal-case-too-manish-sisodia-lawyer-on-bail-order-6298892%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Here's%20To%20Tribals%20And%20Their%20Endless%20Fight%20For%20Jal%2C%20Jungle%2C%20Zameen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fcdi3h4s_tribals_625x300_09_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20lot%20going%20on%20this%20week.%20Opposition%20parties%20united%20in%20their%20demand%20to%20ask%20the%20government%20to%20roll%20back%2018%25%20GST%20on%20life%20and%20health%20insurance%20-%20an%20issue%20affecting%2045%20crore%20of%20the%20middle%20class.%20Banner%20headlines%20from%20Bangladesh.%20Vinesh%20Phogat.%20The%20silver%20lining%20of%20Neeraj%20Chopra%20and%20Indian%20hockey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20of%20this%2C%20some%20subjects%20do%20not%20get%20the%20column%20centimetres%20they%20deserve%20in%20newspapers%2C%20nor%20do%20they%20make%20for%20content%20for%20clickbaits.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2029%20June%20this%20year%2C%20a%20young%20MP%20from%20the%20Bharat%20Adivasi%20Party%2C%20representing%20Banswara%2C%20led%20a%20unique%20march.%20His%20supporters%20carried%20blood%20samples%20in%20protest%20of%20a%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20minister's%20remark%20suggesting%20a%20DNA%20test%20to%20prove%20he%20was%20Hindu.%20The%20young%20MP%20stood%20firm%20-%20they%20were%20Adivasis%20who%20didn't%20need%20a%20DNA%20test%20to%20define%20their%20identity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20today%2C%20on%20International%20Day%20of%20the%20World's%20Indigenous%20Peoples%2C%20your%20columnist%20is%20writing%20about%20an%20issue%2C%20often%20ignored%20-%20tribal%20rights%20in%20the%20last%20decade%20of%20the%20ruling%20dispensation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20begin%2C%20here's%20how%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Tribal%20Affairs%20fared%20in%20India%20Budget%202024%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20word%20'Scheduled%20Tribe'%20appears%20only%20once%20in%20the%20Budget%20speech.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAllocations%20for%20National%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20-%20a%20constitutional%20body%2C%20reduced%20from%20Rs%2022%20crores%20to%20Rs%2020%20crores.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPM%20Jan%20Jatiya%20Vikas%20Mission%20budget%20cut%20by%2062%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAllocations%20for%20the%20National%20Tribal%20Welfare%20Program%20went%20down%20by%2010%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDevelopment%20of%20Particularly%20Vulnerable%20Tribal%20Groups%20(PVTGs)%20received%20only%20Rs%2020%20crore%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisplacement%20And%20Dispossession%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Xaxa%20Committee%20on%20Tribal%20Communities%2C%20over%2040%25%20of%20those%20displaced%20by%20development%20projects%20are%20tribals.%20The%20Forest%20(Conservation)%20Amendment%20Act%2C%202023%2C%20was%20rushed%20through%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20just%2038%20minutes%2C%20with%20only%20four%20MPs%20participating.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Act%20weakens%20clearance%20requirements%20and%20gives%20blanket%20exemptions%2C%20impacting%20forests%2C%20wildlife%2C%20and%20indigenous%20communities.%20Procedurally%2C%20the%20Bill%20should%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%20for%20scrutiny.%20Instead%2C%20it%20was%20sent%20to%20a%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20which%20was%20packed%20with%20BJP%20MPs.%20The%20committee%20approved%20all%20amendments%20despite%20six%20MPs%20submitting%20dissent%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20June%202022%20and%20July%202024%2C%20over%201%2C000%20projects%20received%20forest%20clearances%2C%20while%20only%20six%20projects%20were%20denied%20clearance%20between%202018%20and%202022.%20Interestingly%2C%20at%20least%20four%20companies%20that%20topped%20the%20list%20of%20electoral%20bond%20donors%20are%20notorious%20for%20violating%20forest%20and%20tribal%20rights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestions%20in%20Parliament%20have%20revealed%20that%20the%20Great%20Nicobar%20Project%20worth%20Rs%2072%2C000%20crores%20will%20lead%20to%20a%20felling%20of%2010%20lakh%20trees%20and%20alter%20the%20face%20of%20the%20Ecologically%20Sensitive%20Area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsider%20this%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Tribal%20Council%20of%20Nicobar%20Island%20withdrew%20its%20No-Objection%20Certificate%20for%20the%20project.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Government%20hasn't%20consulted%20the%20original%20inhabitants-the%20Shompens%20(a%20PVTG%20tribe)%20and%20the%20Nicobarese.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Anthropological%20Survey%20of%20India%20wasn't%20consulted%20either.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMisgovernance%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20secured%20the%20rights%20of%20people%20from%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%20in%20India.%20But%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%20tells%20a%20different%20story.%20Eklavya%20Model%20Residential%20Schools%20have%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20vacancies%20across%20the%20country.%20Announced%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20Venture%20Capital%20Fund%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(VCF-ST)%20is%20still%20not%20operational.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocio-economic%20indicators%20for%20the%20ST%20population%20in%20India%20are%20also%20worrying.%20Six%20out%20of%2010%20ST%20women%20and%20seven%20out%20of%2010%20ST%20children%20are%20anaemic.%20Four%20out%20of%2010%20children%20over%20six%20years%20of%20age%20have%20had%20no%20schooling.%20Five%20out%20of%2010%20of%20the%20ST%20population%20belong%20to%20the%20lowest%20wealth%20quintile.%20Crimes%20against%20STs%20increased%20by%2014%25%2C%20with%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Maharashtra%20recording%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20assault%20cases%20on%20ST%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHomogenisation%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20put%20out%20a%20book%20called%20Contributions%20of%20Tribal%20Leaders%20in%20the%20Freedom%20Struggle.%20The%20book%20which%20faced%20sharp%20criticism%20for%20downplaying%20Adivasi%20resistance%20to%20caste%20structures%2C%20is%20a%20replica%20of%20an%20e-book%20by%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vanvasi%20Kalyan%20Ashram%20(ABVKA%2C%20an%20RSS%20affiliate%20focused%20on%20organising%20religious%20events%20in%20tribal%20areas).%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20NCST%20was%20led%20by%20a%20former%20member%20of%20the%20ABVKA.%20In%20fact%2C%20both%20BJP%20and%20RSS%20commonly%20ref