2Donald%20Trump%20Agrees%20To%20Debate%20Kamala%20Harris%3A%20What%20Latest%20Polls%20Suggest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20Republican%20presidential%20candidate%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20agreed%20to%20debate%20his%20Democratic%20counterpart%20Kamala%20Harris%20on%20September%2010.%20The%20showdown%20is%20set%20to%20be%20hosted%20by%20ABC%2C%20with%20additional%20debates%20proposed%20for%20September%204%20and%20September%2025%20on%20Fox%20and%20NBC%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20be%20the%20first%20face-off%20between%20the%20two%20rivals%2C%20with%20polls%20indicating%20a%20closely%20contested%20race.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%20vs%20Harris%3A%20What%20polls%20predict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIpsos%20poll%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20Ipsos%20poll%20published%20on%20August%209%2C%20shows%20Kamala%20Harris%20leading%20Donald%20Trump%2042%20per%20cent%20to%2037%20per%20cent%20for%20the%20November%205%20elections.%20This%20shows%20growth%20in%20her%20popularity%20since%20a%20July%2022-23%20Reuters%2FIpsos%20survey%2C%20which%20found%20her%20up%2037%20per%20cent%20to%2034%20per%20cent%20over%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20poll%2C%20Ipsos%20found%20Harris%20leading%20Trump%2042%20per%20cent%20to%2040%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20seven%20states%20where%20the%20election%20was%20closest%20in%202020%20-%20Arizona%2C%20Georgia%2C%20Michigan%2C%20Nevada%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20Pennsylvania%20and%20Wisconsin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EYouGov%20poll%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20CBS%2FYouGov%20poll%20released%20on%20August%204%20shows%20Kamala%20Harris%20levelling%20up%20with%20Donald%20Trump.%20She%20has%20erased%20Trump's%20growing%20lead%20since%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20dropped%20his%20reelection%20bid.%20The%20poll%20indicates%20Harris%20has%20a%201%20per%20cent%20advantage%20over%20Trump%20nationwide%2C%20compared%20to%20Trump's%20previous%20five-point%20edge%20over%20Biden.%20In%20swing%20states%2C%20Harris%20and%20Trump%20are%20equal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20poll%20shows%20only%2051%20per%20cent%20of%20respondents%20thought%20Trump%20was%20mentally%20capable%20of%20the%20presidency%2C%20compared%20to%2064%20per%20cent%20for%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMarist%20poll%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20NPR%2FPBS%20News%2FMarist%20poll%20shows%20Harris%20has%20a%2051-48%20per%20cent%20edge%20over%20Trump%20among%20key%20demographics%20such%20as%20Black%20voters%2C%20white%20women%20with%20college%20degrees%20and%20women%20who%20identify%20as%20political%20independents.%20Independent%20women%20voters%20are%20crucial%20swing%20voters.%20Harris%20has%20made%20significant%20inroads%20with%20this%20group%2C%20leading%20Trump%20by%209%20points%20(53-44%20per%20cent).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20also%20states%20that%20Harris%20has%20made%20significant%20gains%20in%20suburban%20areas%20and%20among%20white%20voters%20overall%2C%20which%20has%20helped%20her%20improve%20her%20standing%20compared%20to%20earlier%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Trump%20still%20maintains%20an%20advantage%20on%20economic%20issues%2C%20leading%20Harris%20by%203%20points%20(51-48%20per%20cent).%20Trump%20also%20leads%20Harris%20on%20handling%20immigration%2C%20with%20a%2052-46%20per%20cent%20advantage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20abortion%2C%20Harris%20has%20a%20clear%20advantage%2C%20leading%20Trump%20by%2015%20points.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamala%20Harris%2C%20who%20entered%20the%20presidential%20race%20on%20July%2021%20after%20receiving%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20endorsement%2C%20has%20selected%20Tim%20Walz%2C%20the%20Governor%20of%20Minnesota%2C%20as%20her%20running%20mate.%20This%20move%20comes%20after%20Biden%20folded%20his%20campaign%20and%20exited%20the%20race%20following%20a%20disastrous%20debate%20performance%20against%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20June%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20and%20Walz%20debuted%20their%20joint%20campaign%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Philadelphia%2C%20marking%20the%20beginning%20of%20their%20bid%20to%20take%20on%20Republican%20Trump%20and%20his%20running%20mate%2C%20JD%20Vance%2C%20in%20the%20upcoming%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723186140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fknofc75_donald-trump-kamala-harris_625x300_31_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-presidential-elections-donald-trump-agrees-to-debate-kamala-harris-what-latest-polls-suggest-6298163%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20Republican%20presidential%20candidate%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20agreed%20to%20debate%20his%20Democratic%20counterpart%20Kamala%20Harris%20on%20September%2010.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-presidential-elections-donald-trump-agrees-to-debate-kamala-harris-what-latest-polls-suggest-6298163%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Venezuelan%20president%20bans%20X%20for%2010%20days%20over%20Musk%20row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723177340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1584%2Flive%2F2519e780-5603-11ef-9fed-43045f136ddb.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc5ypx0p84rgo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nicol%C3%A1s%20Maduro%20and%20X%20owner%20Elon%20Musk%20have%20traded%20barbs%20since%20last%20month's%20disputed%20presidential%20vote.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc5ypx0p84rgo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc5ypx0p84rgo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%