0in%20glass%20bottles%20instead%20of%20plastic%20bottles%2C%20avoid%20paper%20and%20plastic%20straws%2C%20cut%20tissue%20papers%20into%20half%20as%20tissues%20are%20often%20not%20used%20fully%20by%20guests.%20They%20do%20not%20serve%20packaged%20food%2C%20even%20if%20it%20impacts%20their%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.51_11zon-1723128404.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20their%20caf%C3%A9%2C%20discarded%20wood%20is%20transformed%20into%20lamps%2C%20dining%20tables%2C%20and%20staircases.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.51_11zon-1723128404.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.51_11zon-1723128404-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.51_11zon-1723128404-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.51_11zon-1723128404-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.51_11zon-1723128404-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360441%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20their%20caf%C3%A9%2C%20discarded%20wood%20is%20transformed%20into%20lamps%2C%20dining%20tables%2C%20and%20staircases.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20serve%20water%20in%20stainless%20steel%20glasses%20with%20only%20the%20amount%20required%20being%20poured%20to%20prevent%20water%20wastage%2C%20and%20offer%20refills%20if%20needed.%20They%20use%20porcelain%20utensils%2C%20some%20of%20which%20are%2013%20years%20old.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20live%20on%20a%20hill%20in%20a%20delicate%20ecosystem%2C%20and%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20endanger%20the%20local%20wildlife%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amit%20explains%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20Lansdowne%20lacks%20a%20proper%20waste%20disposal%20system.%20To%20tackle%20the%20same%2C%20they%20have%20created%20a%20pit%20to%20manage%20their%20wet%20waste%20behind%20their%20caf%C3%A9%2C%20which%20is%20then%20converted%20into%20compost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9COur%20primary%20responsibility%20is%20to%20wildlife%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20keep%20the%20forest%20vibrant%20and%20healthy%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20planted%20a%20variety%20of%20local%20flora%20including%20Banj%20Oak%2C%20Horse%20Chestnut%2C%20Kafal%2C%20Rhododendron%2C%20and%20Deodar%20Cedar.%20They%20have%20also%20set%20up%20a%20special%20birdbath%20that%20attracts%20local%20species%20such%20as%20Blue%20Whistling%20Thrushes%2C%20Black-headed%20Jays%2C%20and%20Red-billed%20Blue-Magpies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20spot%20provides%20a%20safe%20haven%20from%20larger%20predators%20like%20vultures%20and%20eagles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20many%20larger%20caf%C3%A9s%2C%20this%20one%20does%20not%20rely%20on%20genset%20generators%20for%20backup%20power.%20The%20reason%20is%20that%20these%20generators%20produce%20a%20humming%20noise%20that%20can%20disturb%20the%20local%20birdlife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLiving%20in%20a%20forest%2C%20our%20primary%20responsibility%20is%20to%20the%20birds%2C%20leopards%2C%20mountain%20goats%2C%20wild%20boars%2C%20and%20other%20wildlife%20that%20call%20this%20place%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amit%20explains.%20To%20protect%20the%20surrounding%20animals%2C%20they%20keep%20the%20caf%C3%A9%E2%80%99s%20lighting%20dim%20and%20the%20music%20at%20a%20low%20volume.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20their%20