nt%20of%20the%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fmaratha-heritage-1-1722864134.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20tents%2C%20wadas%2C%20and%20royal%20carts%2C%20Chavni%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20Maratha%20era%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fmaratha-heritage-1-1722864134.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fmaratha-heritage-1-1722864134-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fmaratha-heritage-1-1722864134-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fmaratha-heritage-1-1722864134-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fmaratha-heritage-1-1722864134-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359855%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20tents%2C%20%3Cem%3Ewadas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20royal%20carts%2C%20Chavni%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20Maratha%20era%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Karlekar%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20important%20enjoyed%20these%20privileges%2C%20ordinary%20people%20would%20walk%20on%20foot.%20But%20providing%20some%20respite%20to%20them%20were%20the%20%3Cem%3Echavnis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(transit%20camps).%20These%20served%20as%20shelters%20for%20the%20troops%20and%20traders%20for%20when%20night%20fell%20or%20when%20they%20needed%20rest.%20It%20was%20during%20their%20travels%20from%20one%20place%20to%20the%20next%20that%20the%20Marathas%20spent%20a%20substantial%20chunk%20of%20their%20time%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201600s%2C%20an%20observer%20looking%20from%20the%20top%20of%20the%20Lohagad%20fort%20would%20be%20privy%20to%20a%20beautiful%20scene%20of%20these%20caravans%20spinning%20a%20colossal%20web%20across%20the%20terrain.%20There%20was%20no%20denying%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3Echavnis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eheld%20a%20certain%20mystique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20destination%20was%20sometimes%20uncertain%20but%20as%20food%20was%20cooked%20and%20jokes%20shared%2C%20some%20of%20the%20most%20beautiful%20friendships%20were%20struck.%20The%20desire%20to%20recreate%20those%20experiences%20in%20the%20present%20day%20is%20what%20compelled%20Karlekar%20and%20Shetye%20to%20set%20their%20eyes%20on%20this%20piece%20of%20land%20in%202017.%20And%20in%202019%2C%20the%20work%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20design%20process%2C%20the%20guiding%20script%20was%20to%20build%20a%20space%20that%20was%20rooted%20in%20Indianness%2C%20says%20Shetye.%20%E2%80%9CChavni%20is%20a%20concept%20that%20subtly%20nurtures%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20architectural%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F119761%2Fqueen-ahilyabai-holkar-maratha%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultural%20legacy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20does%20this%20while%20offering%20a%20tangible%20framework%20for%20the%20hospitality%20and%20tourism%20industry%20in%20Maharashtra.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELive%20like%20a%20Maratha%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarlekar%20and%20Shetye%20have%20been%20urban%20planners%20for%20two%20decades%20now%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20sustainable%20architecture.%20Chavni%20imbues%20these%20concepts%20in%20the%20form%20of%20its%20mini%20carts%2C%20seven%20royal%20tents%2C%20five%20luxury%20carts%2C%20and%20a%20two-bedroom%20classic%20suite%20(%3Cem%3Ewada%3C%2Fem%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20the%20stays%20are%20designed%20on%20the%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%98being%20in%20transit%E2%80%99.%20Tribes%20throughout%20history%20have%20always%20moved%20from%20one%20place%20to%20another%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Karlekar.%20It%20was%20this%20rhythm%20of%20movement%2C%20she%20says%2C%20that%20separated%20the%20opulent%20Moghuls%20from%20the%20simpler%20Marathas.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20latter%20only%20carried%20as%20much%20as%20they%20required%20and%20depended%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F279565%2Ftraditional-indian-food-for-summer-roohafza-sherbet-kokum-sattu-buy-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20local%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20grain%2C%20and%20vegetables%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20their%20needs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20same%20ethos%20is%20championed%20at%20Chavni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-3-1722512407.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20royal%20carts%20are%20imbued%20in%20luxury%20and%20are%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20regions%20of%20Bara%20Maval%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-3-1722512407.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-3-1722512407-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-3-1722512407-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-3-1722512407-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-3-1722512407-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359346%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20royal%20carts%20are%20imbued%20with%20luxury%20and%20are%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20regions%20of%20Bara%20Maval%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Karlekar%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20for%20instance%20the%20royal%20carts.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20a%20side%20of%20history%3A%20The%20native%20chieftains%20of%20Bara%20Maval%20(the%20land%20where%20Chavni%20stands)%20were%20the%20Deshmukhs%2C%20and%20the%20royal%20carts%20are%20named%20after%20the%20five%20Maval%20sub-regions%20%E2%80%94%20Rohida%20Khore%2C%20Hirdas%20Maval%2C%20Gunjan%20Maval%2C%20Pavan%20Maval%2C%20and%20Nane%20Maval.%20Karlekar%20shares%20that%20the%20carts%20are%20real%20bullock%20carts%20with%20wheels.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20wish%20to%20get%20them%20moving%20to%20a%20different%20location%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20say%20Konkan%2C%20we%20can%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20have%20been%20curated%20with%20Indian%20rosewood%20(%3Cem%3Eshisham%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20bamboo%2C%20jute%2C%20and%20brass.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-4-1722512527.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Rahuti%20tents%20are%20decorated%20with%20traditional%20upholstery%20and%20artistry%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-4-1722512527.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-4-1722512527-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-4-1722512527-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-4-1722512527-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-4-1722512527-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359348%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Rahuti%20tents%20are%20decorated%20with%20traditional%20upholstery%20and%20artistry%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Karlekar%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rahuti%20tents%20meanwhile%20are%20decorated%20in%20pieces%20of%20Nizami%20artistry%20with%20Himroo%20(a%20fabric%20made%20of%20silk%20and%20cotton)%20carpets.%20Compared%20to%20the%20royal%20carts%2C%20these%20are%20smaller%20dwellings.%20Each%20tent%20has%20a%20%3Cem%3Echarpoy%20%3C%2Fem%3E(traditional%20woven%20bed)%2C%20flame%20lamps%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341205%2Fbamboo-furniture-gujarat-professor-patented-chair-sustainable-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20upholstery%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20tents%20are%20perfect%20for%20a%20bonfire%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sarja-Raja%20mini%20carts%20are%20tucked%20away%20on%20relatively%20higher%20terrain%20and%20offer%20a%20commanding%20view%20of%20the%20surroundings.%20These%20stays%20are%20perfect%20for%20hikers%20and%20no-fuss%20trekkers%2C%20looking%20to%20have%20an%20immersive%20experience%20with%20minimal%20luxuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-5-1722512900.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Yashwant%20Wada%20is%20designed%20according%20to%20the%20stays%20of%20the%20chieftains%20of%20the%2017th%20century%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-5-1722512900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-5-1722512900-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-5-1722512900-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2F