e%20are%20standard%20books%20available%20in%20both%20languages%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20good%20study%20material%20for%20subjects%20like%20Environment%20and%20Ecology.%20I%20tried%20reading%20booklets%20offered%20by%20other%20coaching%20institutes%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20they%20had%20vocabulary%20and%20grammatical%20errors%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vikas%2C%20who%20eventually%20referred%20to%20the%20booklet%20by%20the%20Shankar%20IAS%20academy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Optimise%20sources%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikas%20says%20that%20many%20Hindi%20medium%20aspirants%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358409%2Fupsc-cse-aspirant-all-six-attempts-failed-kalaripayattu-martial-arts-teacher-startup-kajal-srivastava-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunable%20to%20clear%20the%20prelims%20%3C%2Fa%3Estage%20itself.%20He%20says%20that%20he%20joined%20a%20coaching%20institute%20and%20only%20relied%20on%20coaching%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20read%20the%20standard%20books%20like%20Polity%20by%20M%20Laxmikanth%20and%20Modern%20History%20Spectrum.%20Learn%20to%20optimise%20your%20notes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20need%20to%20understand%20what%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20study.%20Conduct%20a%20trend%20analysis%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20questions%20that%20are%20asked%20in%20both%20prelims%20and%20Mains.%20Prepare%20accordingly.%20Do%20not%20waste%20your%20time%20mugging%20up%20from%20various%20sources.%20Once%20you%20learn%20filtering%20out%20important%20information%2C%20then%20the%20syllabus%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20vast%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Do%20not%20neglect%20current%20affairs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsually%20aspirants%20are%20advised%20to%20read%20The%20Hindu%20or%20The%20Indian%20Express%20newspapers%20%E2%80%93%20both%20available%20only%20in%20English.%20Vikas%20says%2C%