ds-himachal-pradesh-snowfall%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efarm%20fresh%20apples%3C%2Fa%3E%20sold%20by%20my%20parents.%20I%20had%20seen%20the%20painstaking%20efforts%20taken%20by%20my%20parents%20to%20grow%20these%20apples%20firsthand.%20Yet%2C%20someone%20else%20was%20benefiting%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aprajita%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20gave%20birth%20to%20a%20desire%20to%20help%20her%20parents%20which%20fructified%20four%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20move%20to%20Noida%20a%20few%20years%20later%20had%20a%20pivotal%20role%20to%20play%20in%20the%20engineer%20unearthing%20her%20passion.%20Fond%20of%20decoration%20and%20plants%2C%20she%20started%20growing%20them.%20She%20was%20a%20natural%20at%20it%20and%20her%20home%20was%20soon%20filled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20friends%20started%20asking%20me%20for%20ways%20to%20grow%20and%20take%20care%20of%20plants.%20Since%20this%20was%20a%20much%20asked%20question%2C%20I%20started%20sharing%20tips%20on%20home%20decor%20and%20growing%20indoor%20plants%20on%20Instagram%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Aprajita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20compost%20for%20plants%20and%20tending%20to%20them%20also%20led%20her%20into%20the%20world%20of%20sustainability.%20Back%20home%20in%20Himachal%2C%20climate%20change%20had%20adversely%20impacted%20their%20produce%20as%20well.%20She%20started%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20combat%20it%2C%20starting%20with%20a%20shift%20to%20natural%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20returned%20home%20in%20July%202021%2C%20the%20harvest%20season%2C%20she%20found%20that%20her%20parents%20were%20struggling%20to%20get%20the%20right%20price%20for%20their%20produce.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20we%20had%20to%20go%20to%20Delhi%20to%20sell%20our%20apples.%20Later%2C%20%3Cem%3Emandis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eopened%20up%20in%20Himachal.%20Due%20to%20middlemen%2C%20no%20farmer%20ever%20gets%20the%20full%20value%20that%20he%20deserves.%20After%20my%20daughter%20started%20selling%20it%20online%2C%20things%20have%20completely%20changed.%20I%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20market%20rate%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arun%20Bansal%2C%20who%20has%20been%20farming%20since%201986.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPained%20by%20what%20she%20saw%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20help%20her%20father%20get%20the%20right%20price.%20She%20asked%20her%20Instagram%20community%20(which%20was%20then%20about%2010%2C000)%20if%20they%20would%20be%20willing%20to%20buy%20their%20apples%2C%20freshly%20plucked%20from%20the%20farm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aprajita%20Bansal%20runs%20Phal%20Phool%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20sells%20apples%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359935%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAprajita%20runs%20Phal%20Phool%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20sells%20apples%20grown%20in%20her%20family%20orchard.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20her%20pleasant%20surprise%2C%20the%20response%20was%20overwhelmingly%20positive.%20She%20hosted%20a%20sale%2