0on%20creating%20a%20food%20forest%20on%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20her%20parents%E2%80%99%20land.%20Here%2C%20she%20is%20growing%20different%20varieties%20of%20native%20trees%20and%20plants.%20She%20collects%20heirloom%20seeds%20from%20across%20the%20country%20and%20grows%20them%20in%20their%20orchard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20remains%20confident%20that%20the%20soil%20will%20be%20in%20great%20condition%20in%20the%20next%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20apples%20are%20more%20prone%20to%20insect%20bites%20now%20and%20many%20get%20damaged%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20satisfied%20that%20we%20are%20giving%20poison-free%20fruits%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aprajita%2C%20for%20whom%20life%20has%20indeed%20come%20full%20circle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Aprajita%20Bansal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722939423000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D359926%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aprajita%20Bansal%20runs%20Phal%20Phool%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20sells%20apples%20and%20other%20products%20grown%20on%20her%20family%20orchard%20in%20Banon%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20By%20eliminating%20middlemen%2C%20she%20has%20ensured%20that%20her%20father%20earns%20three%20times%20the%20profit%20while%20customers%20get%20farm%20fresh%20apples.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Life%20of%20a%20Champion%3A%20Javelin%20Star%20Neeraj%20Chopra%E2%80%99s%20Historic%20Career%20That%20Led%20Him%20To%20Paris%20Olympics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENeeraj%20Chopra%2C%20hailing%20from%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Khandra%20village%2C%20began%20his%20athletic%20journey%20after%20a%20chance%20encounter%20with%20javelin%20throw.%20Despite%20financial%20challenges%2C%20his%20dedication%20and%20talent%20made%20him%20the%20first%20Asian%20to%20win%20Olympic%20gold%20in%20athletics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Olympic%20Stadium%20in%20Paris%20will%20be%20the%20centre%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20attention%20today%20as%20Neeraj%20Chopra%20begins%20his%20quest%20to%20defend%20his%20javelin%20throw%20gold%20medal%20at%20the%202024%20Paris%20Olympics.%20Neeraj%20is%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20medal%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20today%E2%80%99s%20qualification%20round%20for%20the%20men%E2%80%99s%20javelin%20throw%2C%20he%20will%20compete%20against%2032%20athletes%20from%20around%20the%20world.%20If%20he%20advances%2C%20Neeraj%20will%20participate%20in%20the%20finals%20on%208%20August%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20excitement%20surrounding%20his%20performance%20is%20palpable.%20Last%20week%2C%20Mohak%20Nahta%2C%20CEO%20of%20Atlys%2C%20a%20visa%20application%20platform%2C%20made%20a%20buzzworthy%20offer%20on%20LinkedIn.%20He%20boldly%20pledged%20to%20personally%20arrange%20a%20free%20visa%20to%20any%20country%20for%20everyone%20who%20applies%20for%20one%20full%20day%20if%20Neeraj%20Chopra%20wins%20gold%20at%20the%20Olympics!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20journey%20Neeraj%20had%20to%20traverse%20to%20become%20the%20celebrated%20champion%20he%20is%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Sarpanch%E2%80%99%2C%20weight%20loss%20and%20javelin%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Khandra%20village%20in%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Panipat%20district%2C%20Neeraj%20comes%20from%20a%20farming%20family.%20Khandra%20has%20around%202%2C000%20residents%20who%20are%20mostly%20farmers.%20His%20father%20Satish%20Kumar%20is%20a%20farmer%2C%20and%20his%20mother%20Saroj%20Devi%20is%20a%20housewife.%20He%20has%20two%20sisters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20earned%20the%20nickname%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ESarpanch%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(village%20head)%20after%20wearing%20a%20new%20%3Cem%3Ekurta%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20gifted%20by%20his%20father%2C%20to%20college.%20His%20friends%20started%20calling%20him%20by%20this%20nickname%20that%20day%2C%20and%20it%20has%20stuck%20with%20him%20ever%20since!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20journey%20into%20sports%20began%20in%202009%20with%20a%20personal%20goal%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F260253%2Fneeraj-chopra-olympic-gold-video-viral-twitter-haryana-first-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20lose%20some%20excess%20weight.%3C%2Fa%3E%20A%2012-year-old%20Neeraj%20weighed%2090%20kg%20and%20had%20little%20interest%20in%20exercising.%20Encouraged%20by%20his%20family%20to%20take%20fitness%20seriously%2C%20he%20began%20his%20athletic%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20serendipitous%20encounter%20with%20javelin%20thrower%20Jai%20Choudhary%20during%20a%20morning%20run%20made%20Neeraj%20see%20his%20own%20potential%20in%20the%20sport.%20Though%20pursuing%20athletics%20required%20his%20family%20to%20invest%20considerable%20savings%2C%20his%20unwavering%20dedication%20and%20ability%20to%20overcome%20injuries%20and%20setbacks%20turned%20him%20into%20one%20of%20the%20most%20distinguished%20athletes%20in%20the%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20youth%20prodigy%20to%20Olympic%20and%20World%20Champion%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20a%2016-year-old%20Neeraj%20earned%20a%20silver%20medal%20in%20the%20Youth%20Olympics%20quarterfinals%20in%20Bangkok.%20During%20the%202016%20IAAF%20World%20U20%20Championships%20in%20Bydgoszcz%2C%20Poland%2C%20he%20secured%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F62646%2Fneeraj-chopra-javelin-u20-world-record%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egold%20medal%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20throw%20of%2086.48m%2C%20setting%20a%20new%20under-20%20world%20record%2C%20drawing%20global%20attention%20to%20his%20talent.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20his%20breakthrough%20came%20in%202017%20when%20he%20claimed%20gold%20at%20the%20Asian%20Athletics%20Championship.%20Later%2C%20he%20also%20won%20gold%20at%20the%202018%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20to%20win%20the%20javelin%20throw%20at%20the%20event%2C%20as%20well%20as%20at%20the%20Jakarta%202018%20Asian%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20journey%20to%20becoming%20a%20sports%20star%2C%20Neeraj%20has%20trained%20under%20Australian%20coach%20Garry%20Calvert%20at%20the%20Olympic%20Training%20Centre.%20Despite%20overcoming%20numerous%20obstacles%20to%20achieve%20top-tier%20status%2C%20Neeraj%20credits%20his%20success%20to%20this%20comprehensive%20support%20system.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CGarry%20sir%20has%20been%20a%20huge%20source%20of%20knowledge%20and%20help%E2%80%A6%20and%20my%20parents%20have%20always%20backed%20me%20to%20push%20myself%20to%20be%20the%20best%20in%20whatever%20it%20is%20that%20I%20do.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2026%2C%20Neeraj%20is%20a%20leading%20javelin%20thrower.%20As%20the%20current%20Olympic%2C%20World%2C%20and%20Asian%20Games%20javelin%20champion%2C%20he%20made%20history%20as%20the%20first%20Asian%20to%20win%20an%20Olympic%20gold%20in%20javelin%20at%202020%20Tokyo%20Olympics%20%E2%80%94%20joining%20Abhinav%20Bindra%20as%20one%20of%20just%20two%20Indians%20to%20achieve%20individual%20Olympic%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Neeraj%20has%20added%20gold%20medals%20from%20the%202022%20Diamond%20League%2C%20the%202022%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20and%20the%202023%20World%20Championships%20in%20Budapest%20to%20his%20collection.%20The%20victory%20at%20Budapest%20made%20him%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20world%20champion%20in%20any%20athletics%20discipline.%20He%20also%20made%20history%20as%20the%20first%20Indian%20to%20win%20at%20the%20World%20Under-20%20Championships%2C%20establishing%20himself%20as%20one%20of%20the%20all-time%20great%20javelin%20throwers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20accolades%20continued%20with%20the%20Arjuna%20Award%20in%202018%2C%20the%20Vishist%20Seva%20Medal%20(VSM)%20in%202020%2C%20the%20Major%20Dhyan%20Chand%20Khel%20Ratna%20Award%20(India%E2%80%99s%20highest%20sporting%20honour)%20in%202021%2C%20the%20Param%20Vishisht%20Seva%20Medal%20(PVSM)%20in%202022%2C%20and%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20(India%E2%80%99s%20fourth%20highest%20civilian%20honour)%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeeraj%E2%80%99s%20consistent%20wins%20on%20the%20grandest%20stages%20have%20established%20him%20as%20a%20top-tier%20javelin%20thrower.%20His%20drive%20to%20improve%20his%20throwing%20distances%20has%20garnered%20him%20a%20massive%20social%20media%20following%2C%20exceeding%20nine%20million%20Instagram%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20self-belief%2C%20the%20javelin%20star%20said%20in%20an%20interview%2C%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%2C%20I%20have%20felt%20that%20my%20throw%20has%20not%20been%20up%20to%20the%20mark%2C%20until%20the%20last%20throw.%20But%20I%20still%20believe%20in%20myself%20that%20I%20have%20to%20do%20it%20till%20the%20end.%20And%20in%20many%20competitions%2C%20my%20last%20throw%20has%20been%20the%20best%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Neeraj%20Chopra%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fneeraj____chopra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40neeraj____chopra%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Folympics.com%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fneeraj-chopra-frequently-asked-questions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENeeraj%20Chopra%3A%20Did%20you%20know%20the%20Olympic%20champion%20is%20known%20as%20%E2%80