heir%20lives%20better%20by%20providing%20them%20jobs%20online%2C%20which%20would%20accord%20them%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20true%20to%20his%20word%2C%20Chandrashekhar%20started%20Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20%E2%80%94%20an%20online%20platform%20providing%20jobs%20for%20daily%20wage%20labourers%2C%20rescuing%20them%20from%20a%20life%20of%20waiting%20on%20the%20streets.%20Over%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20the%20company%20has%20provided%20a%20regular%20income%20to%20over%20one%20lakh%20workers%2C%20according%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20this%20boy%20from%20Ami%20village%20in%20Darbhanga%2C%20Bihar%2C%20brought%20change%20to%20the%20lives%20of%20lakhs%20of%20migrant%20labourers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20should%20workers%20migrate%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20very%20rural%20part%20of%20Bihar%2C%20in%20a%20village%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F302115%2Fdelhi-doctors-and-volunteers-give-free-healthcare-to-poor-people-on-streets-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elacked%20basic%20facilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20a%20school%20post-Class%205%2C%20Chandrashekhar%20was%20no%20stranger%20to%20poverty.%20He%20saw%20his%20uncle%20move%20to%20different%20cities%20in%20search%20of%20work%20and%20was%20privy%20to%20his%20sufferings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk1-1722844675.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chandrashekhar%20speaking%20to%20labourers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital-labour-chowk1-1722844675.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fdigital